# --- Server-side only. NEVER prefix a secret with EXPO_PUBLIC_ (that ships it in the app bundle). ---
# The /api/enrich proxy reads this. Copy to `.env` and paste your key there.
DEEPSEEK_API_KEY=


# Optional: production proxy origin (your EAS Hosting URL), e.g. https://gym.expo.app
# Leave unset in dev — the app then calls the Metro dev server that serves +api.ts.
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=
